THE START OF A NEW ADVENTURE!
Our kids begin a new chapter in their lives, an adventure that will be memorable in many ways.
We are here to ensure they overcome any challenge.
They are our #1 priority!
Classes are starting on time and online for now.
In person options will begin when allowed by the State of Arizona.
See the FREE education available. 👇
https://colegiopetiteaz.com/

¡Son nuestra prioridad número 1!
Las clases comienzan a tiempo y en línea por ahora.
Las opciones en persona comenzarán cuando lo permita el Estado de Arizona.
Vea la educación GRATUITA disponible. 👇

A NEW SCHOOL YEAR, A NEW NOW, A NEW LEARNING CULTURE!
We are all different today. It is not the same, but it can be better.
Our kids are unique and capable of amazing things, but they need us to show them the way.
Classes are beginning on time and online for now. In person options will begin when allowed by the State of Arizona.

See what we have waiting this school year. 👇
https://colegiopetiteaz.com/

Vea lo que tenemos esperando este año escolar. 👇

A great success! Our 4th Annual Family Dance event this February 2020. More than 200 people took part at one of the biggest events we hold each year. Days of hard work came together on this day and transformed into a great family event! THANK YOU all for your participation, this wouldn’t been possible without your support.

¡Un gran éxito! nuestro 4to Baile Anual Familiar que se llevó acabo este febrero 2020. Más de 200 personas participaron en uno de los eventos más grandes que realizamos cada año. ¡Dias de arduo trabajo se unieron al día y se transformaron en un gran evento familiar! GRACIAS a todos por su participación, esto no hubiera sido posible sin su apoyo.
